:"穿山甲、熊膽、阿膠... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最大問題係D「藥」根本冇用 濫殺動物 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78fc8230f8282da5f71f7a5e9d9328856a021c3b","tid":704005,"uid":143499,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:31:28.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，對住支那人開採或者搶掠你嘅資源，應該好似南非對付偷獵者直接開槍射殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就算曱甴咁低等嘅生物，佢嘅屍體都可以攞嚟餵雞，佢都可以用嚟處理廚餘，所以曱甴喺食物鏈入面係好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係支那人種就完全唔同，佢哋去過嘅地方必定寸草不生而且佢哋根本對地球完全冇貢獻，就算啲屍體攞嚟餵狗都會毒撚死啲狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用泥土或者火化都會污染環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以當年艾森豪威爾話要用核彈炸平北京係絕對正確嘅做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/red.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e9e608aab32b6bf4802b0119b455a5da7e92ab","tid":704005,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:36:45.000Z","msg":"辛巴威享受中國金援最大水電計畫靠中資企業完工-- 上報/ 國際<br />\n<br />\n2018年3月29日 - 辛巴威總統姆南加瓦（Emmerson Mnangagwa）上任後積極改善與中國的關係，加速中國企業負責建造的加勒比（Kariba）南部水電站擴建計畫，28日正式舉行完工典禮，姆南加瓦帶領官員參與，表達對該計畫的重視，也期望中國多協助辛巴威發展能源業。中國藉由「一帶一路」計畫可望延伸、深入在辛巴威的勢力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ori.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=37874\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fori.upmedia.mg%2Fnews_info.php%3FSerialNo%3D37874&d=Xss1rbCGGQoh133a3dErLMKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=52c5ce26\" target=\"_blank\">ori.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=37874</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e75c70b928e3beb69399dce749a7a911e9f1c95","tid":704005,"uid":66119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:40:19.000Z","msg":"反正贏国人食開假野<br />\n用其他平野代替再賣都貴一貴都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295a51b7801b8ae538253271c5aeaded06ba2423","tid":704005,"uid":34300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5c4e7ec97e8a14c7ffda5bd28a724de0ceafa490","tid":704005,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:22:35.000Z","msg":"不過而家都有豬皮膠同牛皮膠啦<br />\n唔好再吹奏一定用阿膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:44:53.000Z","msg":"驢皮膠先係假貨<br />\n<br />\n最初阿膠係用牛皮整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2133a3f36644da183fc14708335fb8b255206e1","tid":704005,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T06:59:35.000Z","msg":"去到邊度都令當地寸草不生"},{"pid":"924feeaae64b3453e8a4d873d144951a7610239c","tid":704005,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a10860946f44e6dccc4c13ed62ca2c6a9d3487","tid":704005,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:06:54.000Z","msg":"一帶一路<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1306892ce7ade07d3bf9b8ba2ece32a78adc773c","tid":704005,"uid":59929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:11:25.000Z","msg":"縱容大陸人入自己國家作惡仲唔係抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd02152ba37ff01e0608746f8fa887d310d7a0d1","tid":704005,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T07:54:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大佬人提煉阿膠竟然用真驢皮做原材料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能一兌十咁落，點都要落小小真野。"},{"pid":"c6800a636fc94b2472e864f7d88ef2c8a1993360","tid":704005,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T08:12:39.000Z","msg":"屠殺豬牛雞又無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a47284c56d8